<html>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/piano.css">
<% include ./partials/header %> 
<div class="container text-center" style='font-family: Palatino'>
<div class='col-md-12'>
<p>See below for my first music app. Browsers don't allow the web music API to autoplay, so please press the button below before starting. Ripped off pretty directly from <a href='https://dev.to/shimphillip/building-a-piano-with-tone-js-5c2f'>here</a> :)
